        },
        "category": "offensive",
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Occult arsenal (DC 40): <em>mind fog</em> round 1 (−2 status Will, 20-ft cloud), a <strong>quickened confusion</strong> (1 action) thrown at a martial <em>every</em> round, <em>greater invisibility</em> round 2, then <strong>dominate</strong> (@Check[type:will|dc:40], incapacitation) — a dominated PC is sent to B19 to pick up the @UUID[Compendium.cotct-pf2e-conversion.cotct-hazards.Actor.soultrapGem00001]{Soultrapping Gem}.</p>"
